  "short_description": "In Wigged Out, two rival schools clash in a wild and wacky ball game! Dodge, jump, and attack, whether by launching a rubber turkey at your foes or netting a goal while riding a goat. Chaos and skill go hand in hand in this fast-paced, laugh-out-loud showdown!",
