  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge into Wigged Out, the historically inaccurate ball game where absurdity reigns and chaos is the name of the game!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/7ac1d3cf881f079e5fbe1fdc139c4f1d.avif?t=1774282489\" width=577 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put on your finest wig and dive into the action in this hilarious party game where dodgeball meets football like never before! Use wacky items, or even your own wig to knock the big ball into your opponent’s goal! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/75286c1dfe0b13c057ba8bb3d025f013.poster.avif?t=1774282489\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/75286c1dfe0b13c057ba8bb3d025f013.webm?t=1774282489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/63deda04591926202bfd908f10fa52f6.avif?t=1774282489\" width=577 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be on guard! The big ball isn't the only target in Wigged Out, you are too. Keep an eye on your opponents, or risk getting knocked down. And if that isn't enough, the environment is also out to get you, so watch out for exploding manholes and rampaging goats!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/e3922d84a0f46d168771976017e3b316.poster.avif?t=1774282489\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/e3922d84a0f46d168771976017e3b316.webm?t=1774282489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/4503277a3a370524e769701587ef6154.avif?t=1774282489\" width=577 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from six quirky characters, each with a unique WigOut power. Charge up your WigOut bar and unleash total mayhem on the pitch!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/d1cfdd710dc764596c00388da1072e21.poster.avif?t=1774282489\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/d1cfdd710dc764596c00388da1072e21.webm?t=1774282489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/28028b52956e43c857650ae453bcbd5a.avif?t=1774282489\" width=577 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play across 80+ colorful levels set in three diverse areas! Battle it out on <i>The Campus</i>, with lush lawns and busy streets. Head to <i>The Countryside</i>, where angry goats roam and alien invasions might occur. Or take on <i>The Country Fair</i>, where you could find yourself in a giant game of pinball!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/8e6dd647f414646985d85953ac66f597.poster.avif?t=1774282489\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/8e6dd647f414646985d85953ac66f597.webm?t=1774282489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/5fe136daa83e0ad5183a9737c105a5d6.avif?t=1774282489\" width=577 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play locally or online for non-stop fun, or add some bots if that’s more your style!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/7f9944af682fea8c0e2c518260635275.poster.avif?t=1774282489\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/7f9944af682fea8c0e2c518260635275.webm?t=1774282489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"WIG FLINGING FRENZY” -</strong> Make use of various wacky items, or even your own wig to launch the big ball into your opponent's goal! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STAY ON HIGH ALERT! –</strong> It’s not just your opponents you need to worry about. Watch out for bursting hydrants, exploding manholes, and a rampaging school mascot goat! Danger lurks at every turn. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNLEASH YOUR WIGOUT POWER! –</strong> Charge up your character’s unique ability and unleash total chaos on the pitch! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CONQUER 80+ LEVELS! –</strong>Explore vibrant arenas, tackle wild challenges, and master an ever-changing mix of items, hazards, and goal types. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNLEASH HILARITY! –</strong> Play locally or online for non-stop fun, or add some bots if that’s more your style!</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge into Wigged Out, the historically inaccurate ball game where absurdity reigns and chaos is the name of the game!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/7ac1d3cf881f079e5fbe1fdc139c4f1d.avif?t=1774282489\" width=577 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put on your finest wig and dive into the action in this hilarious party game where dodgeball meets football like never before! Use wacky items, or even your own wig to knock the big ball into your opponent’s goal! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/75286c1dfe0b13c057ba8bb3d025f013.poster.avif?t=1774282489\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/75286c1dfe0b13c057ba8bb3d025f013.webm?t=1774282489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/63deda04591926202bfd908f10fa52f6.avif?t=1774282489\" width=577 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be on guard! The big ball isn't the only target in Wigged Out, you are too. Keep an eye on your opponents, or risk getting knocked down. And if that isn't enough, the environment is also out to get you, so watch out for exploding manholes and rampaging goats!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/e3922d84a0f46d168771976017e3b316.poster.avif?t=17742824