97.poster.avif?t=1774282489\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/8e6dd647f414646985d85953ac66f597.webm?t=1774282489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/5fe136daa83e0ad5183a9737c105a5d6.avif?t=1774282489\" width=577 height=71 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play locally or online for non-stop fun, or add some bots if that’s more your style!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/7f9944af682fea8c0e2c518260635275.poster.avif?t=1774282489\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1176060/extras/7f9944af682fea8c0e2c518260635275.webm?t=1774282489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>\"WIG FLINGING FRENZY” -</strong> Make use of various wacky items, or even your own wig to launch the big ball into your opponent's goal! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>STAY ON HIGH ALERT! –</strong> It’s not just your opponents you need to worry about. Watch out for bursting hydrants, exploding manholes, and a rampaging school mascot goat! Danger lurks at every turn. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNLEASH YOUR WIGOUT POWER! –</strong> Charge up your character’s unique ability and unleash total chaos on the pitch! </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CONQUER 80+ LEVELS! –</strong>Explore vibrant arenas, tackle wild challenges, and master an ever-changing mix of items, hazards, and goal types. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>UNLEASH HILARITY! –</strong> Play locally or online for non-stop fun, or add some bots if that’s more your style!</p></li></ul>",
